<br>
Even given the longer fights, I think mage and necro soloing can be about equal because of the self regen spells.  I think if the mage has clarity though, he'll out kill the necro.<br>
<br>
And I don't remember who said it, but I <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> love</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> facing casters.  The only casters that ever give me trouble consistantly are clerics.  Mages can be a pain sometimes, and I used to have trouble with necro's until I noticed that I had a 15 poison resist.  They always cast that stupid 160point poison nuke on me and it would always land for full damage.  Druids are annoying if you aren'y ready for them and your pet kills itelf on the damage shield.  Otherwise druids are easy.<br>
<br>
Shamans are great.  I love fighting NPC shaman that do things like cast slow on me and cast disease on my pet.  Sometimes a shaman will slow my pet, which is annoying, but it just means I have to nuke him a little extra.  Wizards?  Maybe a wizard gets to hit me once with a spell, usually my air pet is good for at least one interrupt and by then, it's way too late for the wizard.  Enchanters are a pain if they land charm, otherwise they're like shamans and waste their time casting pointless spells while you just nukem dead.<br>
<br>
Clerics though.. clerics have this annoying tendancy to heal up huge chunks of their own formidable HP and you end up burning through a lot of mana killing them.  Air pets are quite important against clerics.  Clerics also have that really annoying knockback nuke. <p><center><img src= "http://www.geneseo.edu/~dmf1/firesig.jpg"></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill>The Hunt</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center></td></tr></table><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.238<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

